<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>The AI-Ready Leader: A Maturity Framework | Maturity Coach</title>
  <meta name="description" content="AI is not a technology problem. It's a leadership maturity problem. Download the framework that maps five dimensions of AI-ready leadership across four developmental stages.">

  <meta property="og:title" content="The AI-Ready Leader: A Maturity Framework">
  <meta property="og:description" content="Most leaders are adopting AI faster than they're developing the maturity to govern it. This framework changes that.">
  <meta property="og:type" content="website">
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://maturity.coach/ai-ready-leader/">

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Merriweather:wght@400;700&family=Montserrat:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    :root {
      --primary: #6d4aff;
      --primary-dark: #5638cc;
      --primary-light: #e8e8f5;
      --primary-lighter: #f3f0ff;
      --text-dark: #2a2a3e;
      --text-mid: #555568;
      --text-light: #8888aa;
      --bg-white: #ffffff;
      --bg-off: #f8f8fc;
      --bg-lavender: #f3f0ff;
      --bg-dark: #1a1a2e;
      --border: #e0deef;
      --accent-gold: #c9a84c;
      --accent-green: #2ecc71;
      --shadow-sm: 0 2px 8px rgba(109, 74, 255, 0.08);
      --shadow-md: 0 8px 32px rgba(109, 74, 255, 0.12);
      --shadow-lg: 0 16px 48px rgba(109, 74, 255, 0.16);
      --radius: 12px;
      --radius-sm: 8px;
      --radius-lg: 20px;
      --transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
      --max-width: 1140px;
      --font-head: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      --font-body: 'Merriweather', serif;
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; font-size: 16px; }
    body { font-family: var(--font-body); color: var(--text-dark); background: var(--bg-white); line-height: 1.7; overflow-x: hidden; }
    a { color: var(--primary); text-decoration: none; transition: var(--transition); }
    a:hover { color: var(--primary-dark); }
    img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }
    ul { list-style: none; }

    .container { width: 100%; max-width: var(--max-width); margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; }
    .text-center { text-align: center; }

    .eyebrow {
      font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .heading-xl {
      font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.6rem);
      font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.2; color: var(--text-dark); margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .lead-center {
      font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--text-mid); max-width: 620px; margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 10px;
      padding: 16px 36px; background: var(--primary); color: white;
      font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600;
      border: none; border-radius: var(--radius-sm); cursor: pointer;
      transition: var(--transition); text-decoration: none;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--primary-dark); transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: var(--shadow-md); color: white; }
    .btn-primary:active { transform: translateY(0); }
    .btn-primary svg { width: 20px; height: 20px; pointer-events: none; }

    .btn-outline {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; padding: 12px 24px;
      background: transparent; color: var(--primary); font-family: var(--font-head);
      font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 600; border: 2px solid var(--primary);
      border-radius: var(--radius-sm); cursor: pointer; transition: var(--transition); text-decoration: none;
    }
    .btn-outline:hover { background: var(--primary-light); color: var(--primary); }
    .btn-outline svg { width: 16px; height: 16px; pointer-events: none; }

    /* Navbar */
    .navbar {
      position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.92);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px); -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 14px 0;
    }
    .nav-inner { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 24px; }
    .nav-logo {
      font-family: var(--font-head); font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: var(--primary); letter-spacing: -0.5px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; text-decoration: none;
    }
    .nav-logo span { color: var(--text-light); font-weight: 400; }
    .nav-links { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 28px; }
    .nav-links a { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 0.88rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text-mid); }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--primary); }
    .nav-cta {
      font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600;
      padding: 8px 20px; border-radius: var(--radius-sm); background: var(--primary); color: white !important;
    }
    .nav-cta:hover { background: var(--primary-dark); transform: translateY(-1px); }
    .nav-toggle { display: none; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; flex-direction: column; gap: 5px; padding: 8px; }
    .nav-toggle span { width: 22px; height: 2px; background: var(--text-dark); border-radius: 2px; transition: var(--transition); }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .nav-toggle { display: flex; }
      .nav-links {
        position: absolute; top: 100%; left: 0; right: 0; flex-direction: column;
        background: white; padding: 20px 24px; gap: 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); transform: translateY(-10px); opacity: 0; pointer-events: none; transition: var(--transition);
      }
      .nav-links.open { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 1; pointer-events: auto; }
    }

    /* Hero */
    .hero {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg-dark) 0%, #1f1f3a 60%, var(--bg-lavender) 100%);
      padding: 80px 0 64px; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .hero::before {
      content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
      background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 50%, rgba(109,74,255,0.15) 0%, transparent 50%),
                        radial-gradient(circle at 80% 20%, rgba(201,168,76,0.08) 0%, transparent 50%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .hero-inner { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.3fr 1fr; gap: 56px; align-items: center; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
    @media (max-width: 900px) { .hero-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; } }

    .hero-badge {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
      background: rgba(109,74,255,0.15); border: 1px solid rgba(109,74,255,0.3);
      color: #b8a0ff; font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 600;
      padding: 6px 16px; border-radius: 100px; margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .hero-badge svg { width: 14px; height: 14px; pointer-events: none; }

    .hero h1 {
      font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4.5vw, 2.8rem);
      font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.15; color: white; margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .hero h1 .highlight { color: #b8a0ff; }

    .hero-sub { font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #cccce0; max-width: 520px; margin-bottom: 36px; }

    .hero-cta-group { display: flex; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .hero-cta-group { flex-direction: column; }
      .hero-cta-group .btn-primary, .hero-cta-group .btn-outline { width: 100%; justify-content: center; }
    }

    /* Hero stat strip */
    .hero-stats { display: flex; gap: 32px; margin-top: 32px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .hero-stat { text-align: left; }
    .hero-stat-num { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 700; color: #b8a0ff; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .hero-stat-label { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 0.75rem; color: #8888aa; }
    @media (max-width: 480px) { .hero-stats { gap: 20px; } }

    /* Doc preview card */
    .doc-preview {
      background: white; border-radius: var(--radius-lg); overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg); border: 1px solid rgba(109,74,255,0.2); transform: rotate(1deg);
    }
    .doc-cover {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #2a2a5e 50%, #6d4aff 100%);
      padding: 40px 32px; text-align: left; min-height: 280px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center;
    }
    .doc-cover-eyebrow { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #c9a84c; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .doc-cover-title { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 700; color: white; line-height: 1.3; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .doc-cover-sub { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.85rem; color: #aaaacc; font-style: italic; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .doc-cover-author { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 0.78rem; color: #b8a0ff; font-weight: 500; }
    .doc-pages { background: var(--bg-off); padding: 16px 24px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .doc-pages-text { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-mid); }
    .doc-pages-badge { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--accent-green); background: rgba(46,204,113,0.1); padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 100px; }

    /* Form card */
    .form-card {
      background: white; border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 36px 32px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg); border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .form-title { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-dark); margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .form-sub { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-light); margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .form-group { margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .form-group input, .form-group select {
      width: 100%; padding: 13px 16px; border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-sm); font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 0.92rem;
      color: var(--text-dark); background: var(--bg-off); transition: var(--transition);
    }
    .form-group input:focus, .form-group select:focus {
      outline: none; border-color: var(--primary); background: white; box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(109,74,255,0.1);
    }
    .form-group input::placeholder { color: var(--text-light); }
    .form-disclaimer { font-size: 0.76rem; color: var(--text-light); text-align: center; margin-top: 14px; line-height: 1.5; }
    .form-disclaimer a { text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 2px; }
    .form-success { display: none; text-align: center; padding: 20px 0; }
    .form-success.show { display: block; }
    .success-icon { width: 56px; height: 56px; margin: 0 auto 16px; background: var(--primary-light); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
    .success-icon svg { width: 28px; height: 28px; color: var(--primary); pointer-events: none; }
    .success-title { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-dark); margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .success-text { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-mid); margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.6; }

    /* Trust bar */
    .trust-bar { background: var(--bg-off); padding: 32px 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .trust-inner { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 40px; }
    .trust-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text-mid); }
    .trust-item svg { width: 18px; height: 18px; color: var(--primary); flex-shrink: 0; pointer-events: none; }
    @media (max-width: 640px) { .trust-inner { gap: 20px; } .trust-item { font-size: 0.78rem; } }

    /* Dimensions section */
    .dimensions-section { padding: 80px 0; background: white; }
    .dim-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 24px; margin-top: 48px; }
    .dim-card { padding: 32px 28px; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); background: white; transition: var(--transition); position: relative; }
    .dim-card:hover { box-shadow: var(--shadow-md); transform: translateY(-4px); border-color: var(--primary-light); }
    .dim-card-num { position: absolute; top: 20px; right: 24px; font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--primary-light); line-height: 1; }
    .dim-card-icon { width: 44px; height: 44px; background: var(--primary-light); border-radius: var(--radius-sm); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 18px; }
    .dim-card-icon svg { width: 22px; height: 22px; color: var(--primary); pointer-events: none; }
    .dim-card h3 { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-dark); margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .dim-card p { font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--text-mid); }

    /* Stages section */
    .stages-section { padding: 80px 0; background: var(--bg-dark); color: white; }
    .stages-section .eyebrow { color: #b8a0ff; }
    .stages-section h2 { color: white; }
    .stages-section .lead-center { color: #cccce0; }
    .stages-track { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 24px; margin-top: 56px; }
    @media (max-width: 900px) { .stages-track { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }
    @media (max-width: 480px) { .stages-track { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
    .stage-card { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(109,74,255,0.2); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 28px 24px; transition: var(--transition); }
    .stage-card:hover { background: rgba(109,74,255,0.1); border-color: rgba(109,74,255,0.4); }
    .stage-badge { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #b8a0ff; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .stage-card h3 { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; color: white; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .stage-card p { font-size: 0.85rem; color: #aaaacc; line-height: 1.6; }
    .stage-trap { margin-top: 14px; padding-top: 14px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); font-size: 0.8rem; color: #ff6b6b; }

    /* Quote section */
    .quote-section { background: var(--bg-lavender); padding: 72px 0; text-align: center; }
    .quote-text { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 1.3rem; font-style: italic; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--text-dark); max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto 20px; }
    .quote-author { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-mid); }
    .quote-author strong { color: var(--text-dark); font-weight: 600; }

    /* Final CTA */
    .final-cta { background: var(--bg-lavender); padding: 80px 0; text-align: center; }
    .final-cta p { max-width: 520px; margin: 0 auto 32px; color: var(--text-mid); font-size: 1.05rem; }
    .final-cta-meta { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 32px; margin-top: 28px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .final-cta-meta-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-mid); }
    .final-cta-meta-item svg { width: 16px; height: 16px; color: var(--primary); pointer-events: none; }

    /* Footer */
    .footer { background: var(--bg-dark); padding: 48px 0 32px; }
    .footer-inner { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 24px; }
    .footer-brand { font-family: var(--font-head); font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--primary); }
    .footer-brand span { color: white; font-weight: 400; }
    .footer-links { display: flex; gap: 24px; }
    .footer-links a { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 0.85rem; color: #8888aa; }
    .footer-links a:hover { color: white; }
    .footer-copy { text-align: center; margin-top: 32px; padding-top: 24px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-light); }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .hero { padding: 56px 0 48px; }
      .dimensions-section, .stages-section, .quote-section, .final-cta { padding: 56px 0; }
      .form-card { padding: 28px 20px; margin: 0 16px; }
      .doc-preview { margin: 0 16px; }
      .hero-stats { flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; }
    }
    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
      *, *::before, *::after { animation-duration: 0.01ms !important; transition-duration: 0.01ms !important; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- NAVBAR -->
  <nav class="navbar">
    <div class="container nav-inner">
      <a href="https://maturity.coach" class="nav-logo">
        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="#6d4aff" stroke-width="2"/>
          <path d="M12 6L12 18M6 12L18 12" stroke="#6d4aff" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        </svg>
        Maturity<span>.coach</span>
      </a>
      <button class="nav-toggle" aria-label="Toggle menu" onclick="document.querySelector('.nav-links').classList.toggle('open')">
        <span></span><span></span><span></span>
      </button>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="https://maturity.coach/#services">Services</a>
        <a href="https://maturity.coach/#approach">Approach</a>
        <a href="https://maturity.coach/technical-leaders/">Technical Leaders</a>
        <a href="#download" class="nav-cta">Download Free</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero" id="download">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-inner">

        <!-- LEFT: Copy + Stats -->
        <div>
          <div class="hero-badge">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M12 2L2 7L12 12L22 7L12 2Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              <path d="M2 17L12 22L22 17" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              <path d="M2 12L12 17L22 12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
            Free Framework - No Email Gate After Download
          </div>

          <h1>
            AI Is Not a <span class="highlight">Technology</span> Problem.<br>
            It's a <span class="highlight">Leadership Maturity</span> Problem.
          </h1>

          <p class="hero-sub">
            Most leaders are adopting AI faster than they're developing
            the maturity to govern it. This framework maps five dimensions
            of AI-ready leadership across four developmental stages -
            so you know exactly where you are and what comes next.
          </p>

          <div class="hero-stats">
            <div class="hero-stat">
              <div class="hero-stat-num">5</div>
              <div class="hero-stat-label">Leadership Dimensions</div>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-stat">
              <div class="hero-stat-num">4</div>
              <div class="hero-stat-label">Maturity Stages</div>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-stat">
              <div class="hero-stat-num">10</div>
              <div class="hero-stat-label">Pages - 15 Min Read</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="hero-cta-group" style="margin-top: 36px;">
            <a href="#download-form" class="btn-primary">
              Download the Framework
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <path d="M21 15V19C21 20.1046 20.1046 21 19 21H5C3.89543 21 3 20.1046 3 19V15M7 10L12 15M7 10L12 15L17 10M7 10V4H17V10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              </svg>
            </a>
            <a href="#preview" class="btn-outline" style="color: #b8a0ff; border-color: #b8a0ff;">
              See What's Inside
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <path d="M9 18L15 12L9 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- RIGHT: Doc preview + form -->
        <div>
          <div class="doc-preview" style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
            <div class="doc-cover">
              <p class="doc-cover-eyebrow">A Maturity Framework</p>
              <p class="doc-cover-title">The AI-Ready Leader</p>
              <p class="doc-cover-sub">Five dimensions. Four stages. One question: who do you need to become to lead effectively in the machine intelligence era?</p>
              <p class="doc-cover-author">By Eugene Nkomba, PCC, CPCC, MBA</p>
            </div>
            <div class="doc-pages">
              <span class="doc-pages-text">10-page PDF</span>
              <span class="doc-pages-badge">Free Download</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="form-card" id="download-form">
            <div id="formContainer">
              <p class="form-title">Get Instant Access</p>
              <p class="form-sub">No spam. Unsubscribe anytime.</p>

              <form id="aiForm" action="#" method="POST">
                <input type="hidden" name="source" value="ai-ready-leader-landing">
                <input type="hidden" name="tags" value="prospects,ai-framework-downloaded">
                <div class="form-group">
                  <input type="text" name="first_name" placeholder="First name" required autocomplete="given-name">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                  <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Work email" required autocomplete="email">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                  <input type="text" name="company" placeholder="Company (optional)">
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="btn-primary" style="width: 100%;">
                  Send Me the Framework
                </button>
                <p class="form-disclaimer">
                  By downloading, you'll receive occasional insights on AI-era leadership.
                  Unsubscribe anytime. Read our <a href="https://maturity.coach/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>.
                </p>
              </form>
            </div>

            <div class="form-success" id="successContainer">
