  <!-- DIMENSIONS PREVIEW -->
  <section class="dimensions-section" id="preview">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="eyebrow">Inside the Framework</p>
        <h2 class="heading-xl">Five Dimensions of AI-Ready Leadership</h2>
        <p class="lead-center">
          Not skills. Not competencies. Dimensions of maturity -
          capacities that develop over time through reflection,
          challenge, and deliberate practice.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="dim-grid">

        <div class="dim-card">
          <div class="dim-card-num">01</div>
          <div class="dim-card-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
              <path d="M12 6V12L16 14" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Cognitive Sovereignty</h3>
          <p>The capacity to maintain independent judgment when augmented by machine intelligence. Not blind trust, not reflexive skepticism - disciplined awareness of when to trust the machine and when to override it.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="dim-card">
          <div class="dim-card-num">02</div>
          <div class="dim-card-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M3 3H21V21H3V3Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              <path d="M3 9H21M9 21V9" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Decision Architecture</h3>
          <p>The design of systems, protocols, and frameworks that govern how humans and machines share decision-making. Who decides what? When to trust the model? Who bears accountability when things go wrong?</p>
        </div>

        <div class="dim-card">
          <div class="dim-card-num">03</div>
          <div class="dim-card-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M12 22S20 18 20 12V5L12 2L4 5V12C4 18 12 22 12 22Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              <path d="M9 12L11 14L15 10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Ethical Grounding</h3>
          <p>A stable moral framework that holds under pressure, novelty, and speed. Regulations lag behind capability by years. The leader's ethical grounding must be internalized - not a compliance checkbox.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="dim-card">
          <div class="dim-card-num">04</div>
          <div class="dim-card-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M22 12H18L15 21L9 3L6 12H2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Adaptive Capacity</h3>
          <p>The psychological and organizational resilience to lead through continuous, accelerating change. Previous transitions played out over decades. The AI transition is measured in months.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="dim-card">
          <div class="dim-card-num">05</div>
          <div class="dim-card-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M17 21V19C17 16.7909 15.2091 15 13 15H5C2.79086 15 1 16.7909 1 19V21" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
              <path d="M23 21V19C23 17.1362 21.7252 15.5701 20 15.126" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Human-Centric Vision</h3>
          <p>The capacity to articulate a future where AI augments human flourishing rather than replacing it. The leaders remembered from this era won't be the ones who adopted AI fastest - but the ones who used it to elevate human work.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="dim-card" style="background: var(--bg-lavender); border-color: var(--primary-light);">
          <div class="dim-card-icon" style="background: var(--primary); ">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M5 12H19M19 12L12 5M19 12L12 19" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Get All Five</h3>
          <p>Each dimension includes maturity indicators, warning signs, and developmental next steps. Download the full framework to assess yourself across all five.</p>
          <a href="#download-form" class="btn-outline" style="margin-top: 16px;">Download Now</a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- STAGES PREVIEW -->
  <section class="stages-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="eyebrow">The Journey</p>
        <h2 class="heading-xl">Four Stages of AI Leadership Maturity</h2>
        <p class="lead-center">
          Every leader passes through these stages. The question is
          whether you move deliberately - or get stuck.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="stages-track">
        <div class="stage-card">
          <p class="stage-badge">Stage 1</p>
          <h3>AI-Anxious</h3>
          <p>Recognizes AI's importance but feels overwhelmed. AI is a threat or a black box. Decision-making remains traditional.</p>
          <div class="stage-trap">Trap: Paralysis</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stage-card">
          <p class="stage-badge">Stage 2</p>
          <h3>AI-Eager</h3>
          <p>Enthusiastically adopted AI tools but enthusiasm outpaces architecture. Ethics is aspirational, not operational.</p>
          <div class="stage-trap">Trap: Velocity without architecture</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stage-card">
          <p class="stage-badge">Stage 3</p>
          <h3>AI-Integrated</h3>
          <p>Built the architecture. Decision rights clear. Ethical boundaries established. AI augments human judgment systematically.</p>
          <div class="stage-trap">Trap: Complacency</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stage-card">
          <p class="stage-badge">Stage 4</p>
          <h3>AI-Wise</h3>
          <p>Articulated a vision where AI serves human flourishing. Sought out as a voice of wisdom in an era of noise.</p>
          <div class="stage-trap">Trap: Isolation</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- QUOTE -->
  <section class="quote-section">
